2026-05-15T22:39:06.5144399Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-15T22:39:06.5145564Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-15T22:39:06.5146699Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-15T22:39:06.5147767Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-15T22:39:06.5148653Z 33    -->
