2026-05-15T22:39:07.0955672Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-15T22:39:07.0955991Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-15T22:39:07.0956324Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-15T22:39:07.0956677Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
